# WEBTOYS Issue Tracker - Crontab Configuration
# 
# To install:
# 1. Copy this file and replace YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN with actual token from: gh auth token
# 2. Run: crontab -e
# 3. Paste the configuration below
#
# To check if running: tail -f /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.log
#
# IMPORTANT: After system updates, verify paths are still correct:
# - Node.js: /usr/local/bin/node
# - GitHub CLI: /opt/homebrew/bin/gh (referenced in scripts)
# - Claude CLI: /Users/bartdecrem/.local/bin/claude (referenced in scripts)

# Run full pipeline every 3 minutes (reformulate, fix, create PRs)
*/3 * * * * HOME=/Users/bartdecrem GH_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN GITHUB_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN ENABLE_AUTO_FIX=true PROJECT_ROOT=/Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot /usr/local/bin/node /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.js >> /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.log 2>&1

# Alternative configurations:

# Run every 20 minutes (less aggressive)
# */20 * * * * HOME=/Users/bartdecrem GH_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN GITHUB_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN ENABLE_AUTO_FIX=true PROJECT_ROOT=/Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot /usr/local/bin/node /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.js >> /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.log 2>&1

# Run only reformulation (no auto-fix)
# */5 * * * * HOME=/Users/bartdecrem GH_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN GITHUB_TOKEN=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN ENABLE_AUTO_FIX=false PROJECT_ROOT=/Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot /usr/local/bin/node /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.js --reformulate >> /Users/bartdecrem/Documents/code/vibeceo8/sms-bot/agent-issue-tracker/monitor.log 2>&1